title: Crochet! Magazine - Winter 2013
description: This Winter 2013 issue of Crochet! magazine gives you full-color photos, complete instructions, and how-to articles and techniques, all direct to you from our crochet-loving editors. Make the most of those hard-to-come-by crochet moments with foolproof designs in appealing colors, guaranteed to be as much fun to stitch as they are to use (or give as thoughtful gifts!).
